text: Munboksan is a mountain located in Gyeongju, North Gyeongsang Province and Cheongdo County, South Korea. It has an elevation of . It is part of the Yeongnam Alps mountain range. ==See also== *Geography of Korea *List of mountains in Korea *List of mountains by elevation *Mountain portal *South Korea portal ==References== ==External links== * Official website for the Yeongnam Alps Category:Mountains of North Gyeongsang Province Category:Gyeongju Category:Cheongdo County Category:Mountains of South Korea Category:One-thousanders of South Korea
